= Colored Text Files

This extensions requires 'ultraviolet' gem. It prettifies text attachments and
colors them according to this gem.

= Instal Instructions

You'll need the development lib of oniguruma.
* On debian/ubuntu :
<pre>
$ sudo apt-get install libonig2-dev
$ sudo gem install ultraviolet
</pre>
* On fedora/mandriva :
<pre>
$ sudo apt-get install oniguruma-devel
$ sudo gem install ultraviolet
</pre>
